Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.65,0:05:42.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm envious of her...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:45.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,for having a person care for her\Nas much as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:48.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You yourself must have\Nhad a great deal of trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.59,0:05:51.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,as you know, Miss Tanimura,\Nshe can be quite a handful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.60,0:05:55.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I do give you this caution however:\NDo not overstrain yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.19,0:05:58.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you. It's nice to know you care.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.32,0:06:16.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's you! Don't scare me like that!
