Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.13,0:10:24.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.38,0:10:25.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.29,0:10:30.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your students must've been leaping\Nout of their seats. You naughty teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.99,0:10:39.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. Naughty teachers,\Nalways eat their students.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.07,0:10:47.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How many students\Nhave you eaten like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.55,0:10:50.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know. I never counted\Nhow many dicks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.81,0:10:53.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not how many dicks...
