Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.56,0:11:05.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How was Ayano?\NYou already did her, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.36,0:11:08.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about it?
