Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.29,0:11:15.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.35,0:11:24.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There used to be a pair of con-artists\Nwho made a bundle with clever plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.35,0:11:30.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The man-woman duo would aim\Nat rich old people.
