Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.48,0:11:40.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the victim was head-over-heels\Nabout the woman, the man would appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.39,0:11:44.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before the victim knew it, his insurance and securities were transferred to the woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.90,0:11:46.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the old man,\Nstripped of everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.68,0:11:49.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...is placed in a home,\Nfilled with despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.15,0:11:58.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the oldest trick in the book,\Nbut everything's planned out perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.62,0:12:02.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They raked in the cash as the police\Nscratched their heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.66,0:12:04.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-That's an interesting story.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.11,0:12:08.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's hi-tech nowadays,\Nand our industry made sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.34,0:12:11.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we're on top of things\Nwith the latest criminal database.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.45,0:12:13.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, what exactly are you getting to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.42,0:12:16.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A beauty and a beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.28,0:12:25.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just happened to see you playing\Naround with Imada.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.61,0:12:31.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Plus, a while before you two came\Nto this mansion...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.16,0:12:35.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,those con-artists vanished\Nwithout a trace.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.37,0:12:37.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.17,0:12:47.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My job isn't to bust your operations.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.60,0:12:49.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm cool as long as you don't bother me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.98,0:12:52.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Nothing's going to happen.\NI promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.75,0:12:54.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.25,0:12:56.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We finally were able to get in,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.02,0:12:59.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but the previous Master died before we could act...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.28,0:13:03.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...and the successor is that little girl.\NOur plans were ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.04,0:13:08.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All you need to do is switch to the missy\Nand set things on track, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.63,0:13:10.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But this mansion is no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.65,0:13:14.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This mansion is encompassed\Nwith some sort of mysterious magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.58,0:13:18.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think Mistress Ayano is the cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.66,0:13:19.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayano is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.84,0:13:23.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She may look young,\Nbut she's actually fairly old.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.63,0:13:27.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was no need to train her.\NShe was already fully developed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:30.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's making me crazy\Njust by being with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.77,0:13:34.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So? Where did you hide\Nthe jewel in question?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.97,0:13:35.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jewel?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.10,0:13:37.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys didn't steal it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.29,0:13:40.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no point to stealing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.90,0:13:43.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We planned to take\Nthe entire mansion in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.65,0:13:47.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. So that's how it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.28,0:13:50.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know what's up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.82,0:13:52.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.19,0:13:56.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not going along\Nwith this farce any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.46,0:13:59.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mei! Screw this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.48,0:14:01.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're going home! Pack our stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.81,0:14:05.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have asked her to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.81,0:14:11.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Shibata. This was all your doing,\Nwasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.46,0:14:14.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You knew everything from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.07,0:14:16.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Think as you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.06,0:14:18.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This ain't no joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.14,0:14:20.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have a right to be angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:23.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But first, visit Mistress Ayano.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.90,0:14:28.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She has been in bed all day.\NWould you please pay her a visit?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.35,0:14:30.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.44,0:14:33.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I beg of you. For the sake\Nof Mistress Ayano, pay her a visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.85,0:14:37.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of relationship did Mistress Ayano\Nhave with the late Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.29,0:14:42.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They weren't blood-related, were they?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.97,0:14:49.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The two were tied together with a love\Nfar deeper than that of a parent-child.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.46,0:14:53.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The late Master had everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.32,0:14:57.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course he had money.\NTitle and honor as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:15:03.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the only thing he was missing\Nwas a family to love and be loved by.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.93,0:15:05.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When his parents passed away\Nand he become...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.08,0:15:08.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,successor of the Nakakouji name,\Nhe married.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.82,0:15:13.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A son was born unto him,\Nbut it did not last very long.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:18.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One day, during his life of loneliness,\Nthe late Master asked me an odd question:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.16,0:15:22.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Shibata, how would you\Nlike to raise a fairy?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.88,0:15:26.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A fairy? You don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.68,0:15:30.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That girl is a fairy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.57,0:15:37.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it was probably just a figure of speech indicating a girl as lovely as a fairy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.37,0:15:43.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I first met Mistress Ayano\Nat the orphanage, she was like an angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.66,0:15:47.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Without any hesitation, the late Master\Ntook Mistress Ayano in...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.89,0:15:50.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and brought her up under his own care.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.23,0:15:54.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They both loved each other from\Nthe bottom of their hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:16:00.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have never seen such a life filled\Nwith such deep love anywhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.58,0:16:05.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those glorious days continued until\Nthe very day Master passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.07,0:16:09.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the end, the fairy was left incomplete.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:13.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Again, I beg of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.81,0:16:17.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,please, go and cheer\NMistress Ayano up for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.61,0:16:21.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mistress Ayano sees the image\Nof her father in you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:24.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and is yearning to fulfill those desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.10,0:16:26.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You just said...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.16,0:16:29.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that the late Master had a son, right?\NDidn't you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.45,0:16:31.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.45,0:16:32.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.55,0:16:34.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as you think, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:42.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,15, 16, 17, 18, 19, 20.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.14,0:16:47.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How much more is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.17,0:16:52.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A fairy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.25,0:16:58.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That mysterious latency she shows\Nevery so often is like that of a fairy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:17:05.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the father had created a real fairy\Nthrough his own death, then it's an irony.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.47,0:17:12.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like your awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.63,0:17:14.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.84,0:17:19.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shibata asked me to be here.\NHe wanted me to cheer you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.00,0:17:21.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.15,0:17:28.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father, you're finally right by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:30.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here we go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.11,0:17:33.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Listen up. I'm not your father,\Nyou understand that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.03,0:17:36.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, hold me like you used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.98,0:17:38.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.88,0:17:41.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, hold me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.46,0:17:44.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was so lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.46,0:17:46.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I so wanted to see you, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.82,0:17:47.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.64,0:17:52.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father hold me.\NDon't ever let me go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.71,0:17:57.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayano.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.99,0:18:40.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right! Lick me more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.76,0:18:45.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.33,0:19:33.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It feels good. I'm so wet. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:39.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, lick me, don't stop! It feels great.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.09,0:19:43.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You are great...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.81,0:19:47.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't wait, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.26,0:19:53.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry, give it to me, Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.16,0:20:11.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.29,0:20:16.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You are the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.67,0:20:18.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on! It feels so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.44,0:20:26.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am cumming...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.15,0:20:33.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That part... No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.83,0:20:48.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.66,0:20:58.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like this way is a dead end.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.10,0:21:06.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What room is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.20,0:21:09.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A lab or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.44,0:21:12.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this?\NSome sort of drug, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.17,0:21:20.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.24,0:21:23.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well... You know... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.56,0:21:26.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know. You're with that detective,\Naren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.98,0:21:29.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What were you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.67,0:21:31.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I haven't done anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.62,0:21:32.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.49,0:21:34.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said I haven't done anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.15,0:21:38.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fine. I'll ask your body. Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.63,0:22:04.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,May I, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.39,0:22:06.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come in, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.89,0:22:13.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you recalled anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.01,0:22:18.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've had a nostalgic feeling\Never since I set foot in this mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.29,0:22:20.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But now I remember it clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.35,0:22:21.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.18,0:22:25.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a while back,\Nprobably when I was around 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.20,0:22:28.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I lived in this mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.89,0:22:32.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With Mom and a father\Nwhose face I can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.72,0:22:37.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I barely remember walking\Naround the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.19,0:22:41.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were single-parent family,\Nbut we lived a pretty wealthy life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.42,0:22:48.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Mom died,\Nshe left me a large fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.58,0:22:52.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tracing it back,\Nit was the money of Nakakouji.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.92,0:22:58.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You called me here to make\Nme remember that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.78,0:23:02.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The jewel was never lost\Nin the first place, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.38,0:23:04.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it wasn't, just as you surmised.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.45,0:23:06.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.06,0:23:08.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.36,0:23:11.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was some elaborate\Nperformance you put on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.00,0:23:14.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forgive me for all my lack of courtesy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.86,0:23:17.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I assure you, it was\Nnecessary Detective Kido.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.64,0:23:21.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I might as well add another act\Nof insolence and ask you:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.71,0:23:26.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you become the successor\Nto the name of Nakakouji?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.86,0:23:31.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a detective hired to find a jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.27,0:23:34.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And now, I have found the jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.73,0:23:37.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My job is done, it only makes sense\Nthat I go home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.33,0:23:40.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Mistress will be heartbroken.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.50,0:23:43.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When she wakes up, give her my regards.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.85,0:23:44.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So long.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.86,0:23:50.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you're the successor. Fuck that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.90,0:23:51.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.73,0:23:52.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mei!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.51,0:23:54.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that your partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.50,0:23:57.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's my assistant,\Nbut looks like she messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.23,0:24:01.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You fucker. Why'd you come\Nback now, you little prick?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.44,0:24:03.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Calm down. There's no need for violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.73,0:24:04.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.54,0:24:07.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're not going to succeed,\Nthen give the money to me, asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.84,0:24:09.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or else.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.34,0:24:15.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you give yourself out as a clever con-man whose policy was playing it smart?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.03,0:24:16.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It all rides on time and place!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.01,0:24:17.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.82,0:24:21.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.92,0:24:22.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.15,0:24:25.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or you're going to be toast.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.84,0:24:28.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You bitch!\NYou're back-stabbing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.60,0:24:30.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This house is nothing but evil...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.70,0:24:34.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kido, I beg you to take charge\Nof this house, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.45,0:24:36.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,for the sake of Mistress Ayano.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.57,0:24:37.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.34,0:24:40.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The detective business suits my style.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.29,0:24:44.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not the type of character\Nto become master of this family.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.04,0:24:52.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't be Dad's replacement.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.81,0:24:55.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not the person you're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.41,0:24:57.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father, you're leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.10,0:25:04.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't go.\NI've been a very good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.31,0:25:07.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father, you're leaving me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.14,0:25:10.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't want that, I'm so lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.22,0:25:13.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't leave me by myself, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.54,0:25:17.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not your Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.89,0:25:22.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forget about the past and find\Nnew happiness elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.99,0:25:26.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the only thing I can say right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.34,0:25:33.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.92,0:25:47.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.75,0:25:50.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.88,0:25:52.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a fire, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.57,0:26:03.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miss Ayano!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.35,0:26:04.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.29,0:26:10.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like, I can't part\Nfrom this house, either.
